HSBC Global Asset Management (Deutschland) GmbH: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:19 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of HSBC Global Asset Management (Deutschland) GmbH



Snapshot People




Company Overview
HSBC Global Asset Management (Deutschland) GmbH primarily provides its services to institutional, corporate and private clients. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios along with mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets. HSBC Global Asset Management (Deutschland) GmbH is based in Düsseldorf, Germany. It was formed in 1989 and is based in Düsseldorf, Germany. HSBC Global Asset Management (Deutschland) GmbH operates as a subsidiary of HSBC Trinkaus & Burkhardt AG.


Königsallee 21/23Düsseldorf,  40212GermanyFounded in 1989



Phone: 49 0 211 910 4784

Fax: 49 0 211 910 1775

